Package action

Class DiscreteActionDependent

  • java.lang.Object
    • action.DiscreteActionDependent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DiscreteActionInterface, java.lang.Comparable<DiscreteActionInterface>, java.util.Iterator<DiscreteActionInterface>
    public class DiscreteActionDependent
extends java.lang.Object
implements DiscreteActionInterface
    DiscreteActionDependant is the class that allows the creation and the management of a serie (TreeSet) of discrete actions who are dependent The dependence is on the order of insertion in the TreeSet This class is characterized by the following informations :
    • baseAction
    • depentActions is a tree of actions
    • it is an iterator
    • currentAction
